reviewText: A HEALTHY laugh riot all the way, Andal Azhagar Cine Combines' "Engal Anna" is a very different kind of Vijayakanth fare that has come your way this Pongal. This Tamil version of the Malayalam film, "Chronic Bachelor" starring Mammootty, has Prabhu Deva, Pandiarajan and Vadivelu at their comic best, with a serious Vijayakanth adding a humorous touch now and then.
